pg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-white">Jack White</a>宣布他将推出一系列新的 Signature 吉他和 Fender 音箱。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jack-white-no-name-album-review-3781001">Jack White – 《No Name》评论：惊喜专辑是大师自 White Stripes 以来最朋克的作品</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独唱家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-white-stripes">White Stripes</a>主唱与这个传奇吉他品牌合作，推出了两款吉他和一款音箱，每件作品都捕捉到了“原始能量、独特风格、简约的乐器和朋克摇滚精神，这些都定义了 White 辉煌的职业生涯。” ” </p><figure id="attachment_3794490" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794490" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794490" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fenders-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794490" class="wp-caption-text"> Jack White Fender 系列（来源：出版社）</figcaption></figure><p> Signature Jack White 系列包括 Pano Verb 放大器，受到他自己的老式 Vibrasonic 和 Vibroverb 放大器的影响，零售价为 2,869 英镑。该系列还包括 TripleSonic Acoustasonic，其中包括 White 亲自策划的流线型 3 路开关音色 - 售价为 3,499 英镑。</p><p>他还将发布自己的 TripleCaster Telecaster，配有自己的 Jack White 双线圈拾音器、JW-90 单线圈、CuNiFe 宽范围双线圈拾音器、DropTuner、Killswitch 和班卓琴式扶手。 TripleCaster Telecaster 的售价为 2,199 英镑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3794492" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794492" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3794492 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794492" class="wp-caption-text"> Jack White Fender 系列（来源：出版社） </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3794491" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794491" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3794491 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Guitars-3-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794491" class="wp-caption-text"> Jack White Fender 系列（来源：出版社）</figcaption></figure><p>谈到该系列时，怀特说道：“我们发现了旧产品中最好的，新产品中最好的，以及与 Fender 历史相结合的创新，我们认为如果 Leo Fender 今天还活着，他一定会感到非常自豪。” ”。</p><p>杰克·怀特（Jack White）最近惊讶地发布了他的最新专辑，将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-surprise-releases-new-album-in-third-man-shops-encourages-fans-to-share-it-3776576">其放入他的唱片店 Third Man Records 的顾客的包里。</a> </p><figure id="attachment_3794493" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794493" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794493" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Jack-White-Fender-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794493" class="wp-caption-text"> Jack White Fender 系列（来源：出版社）</figcaption></figure><p>随后他于8月2日正式发行了这张专辑， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jack-white-no-name-album-review-3781001"><em>NME</em>给予其四星评价。</a>我们写道：“粉丝们不需要忍受长达 10 个月的无休止的单曲推出、过度饱和的媒体曝光和 TikTok 的肮脏行为，直到他们收到一张他们已经厌倦的专辑。” “这是一首对摇滚乐的神秘性和音乐的乐趣的颂歌，它最生动、最有趣。</p><p> “戏弄并不总能带来满足。直接切入正题吧——这真是一次惊心动魄的旅程。怀特对现实世界的陶醉让现实世界变得更加激动人心。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-london-islington-assembly-hall-photos-footage-setlist-politics-ticket-prices-3793726">杰克·怀特在他最后一刻的亲密伦敦演出中猛烈抨击政客并嘲笑高票价</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-teams-up-with-fender-to-launch-new-signature-guitars-and-amp-3794474">Jack White 与 Fender 合作推出新款签名吉他和音箱</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上亮相。</p> ;
